<p>Basically, if you had asked a speaker, they would have told you that the term you were researching could apply to either a male or female, instead of trying to dig through documents only.</p>
<p>My understanding of that term is &#8220;One of the dawn,&#8221; again, no direct correlation to any one sex. Knowing the language of a people goes much further than one might think&#8230;</p>

